data.text: Pak Jehova Nyasaye, yaye chunya;
Pak Jehova Nyasaye, yaye chunya,
en ema oweyoni richoni duto
oreso ngimani kogolo e bur matut
oromo chunyi gi gik mabeyo
Jehova Nyasaye timo gik makare
Nonyiso Musa timbe mane ochano timo,
Jehova Nyasaye kecho ji kendo ong始won,
Ok osik komanyo ketho kuom ji,
ok otimnwa mowinjore gi richowa
Nimar kaka polo ni malo moyombo piny,
mana kaka wuok chieng始 bor gi podho chieng始,
Mana kaka wuoro kecho nyithinde,
nimar ong始eyo kaka ochweyowa,
Dhano to ndalone chalo gi lum,
to ka yamo okudhe matin nono to kare orumo,
Hera ma Jehova Nyasaye oherogo joma omiye luor,
ma gin joma orito singruokne kendo jogo maparo
Jehova Nyasaye osechungo lochne e polo,
Pakuru Jehova Nyasaye, un malaikane duto,
Pakuru Jehova Nyasaye, un jopolo duto,
Pakuru Jehova Nyasaye, un gik moko duto mochweyo,
